CollectionConverters._`.\n2. Rerun `./gradlew javaTest -Pcoordinates=org.playframework:play-build-link:3.1.0-M1` to confirm the regression is fixed before touching metadata.\n3. If native verification still fails, investigate the `XMLOutputFactory` service-resource registration from the native-trace log and rerun the native trace/test path."}}
